  "elements": [
    {
      "id": "dvHVB5L3obu9XWVFC-q0f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 294.3856729161362,
      "y": 388.7747901109508,
      "width": 1255.05908203125,
      "height": 1275,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a0",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1396247481,
      "version": 2423,
      "versionNonce": 1995883926,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1784520772062,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Online Shopping Platform \n    - Event Driven Architecture with SNS + SQS Fanout architecture for Backend Systems\n\nFunctional Requirements:\n    Public Browse Pages:\n        - Public Browse page with top deals and listings irrsepective of categories\n        - Public Browse page with multiple categories at the top like:\n            - Fashion, Electronics, Appliances, Books, Music etc.\n        - Dedicated public browse page per category\n        - Dedicated public browse page per inventory per category\n            - Item Name, Description, Stock, Seller, Price per unit\n\n   Authentication\n        - Authentication with 3rd Party Provider like Federated Login for Google\n \n\n   Shopping Cart:\n        - Distinct Items, Quanity per Item, Price per Item, Total Price\n        - Available quantity is the difference of available inventory in databse with the overlay of ttl locks of inventory (item_id)\n      \n\n   Address Selection/Entry\n        - Need to understand delivery time base don PinCode\n        - Create/retrieve address\n   \n   \n    Order confirmation/Order review (Order creation with pending status)\n      - Lock inventory with a TTL for user \n\n   \n    Payment Success:\n\n              - Update order confirmation\n\n              - Update inventory (Reduce available quanity), release inventory lock\n\n              - Send Notification\n    \n        \n\nPayment Failure:\n             - Update Order to cancelled, release inventory lock\n             - Send Notification\n\n\nFailure Events: Retries and Compensation mechanisms should be in place\n\n\n              \n\n    ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Online Shopping Platform \n    - Event Driven Architecture with SNS + SQS Fanout architecture for Backend Systems\n\nFunctional Requirements:\n    Public Browse Pages:\n        - Public Browse page with top deals and listings irrsepective of categories\n        - Public Browse page with multiple categories at the top like:\n            - Fashion, Electronics, Appliances, Books, Music etc.\n        - Dedicated public browse page per category\n        - Dedicated public browse page per inventory per category\n            - Item Name, Description, Stock, Seller, Price per unit\n\n   Authentication\n        - Authentication with 3rd Party Provider like Federated Login for Google\n \n\n   Shopping Cart:\n        - Distinct Items, Quanity per Item, Price per Item, Total Price\n        - Available quantity is the difference of available inventory in databse with the overlay of ttl locks of inventory (item_id)\n      \n\n   Address Selection/Entry\n        - Need to understand delivery time base don PinCode\n        - Create/retrieve address\n   \n   \n    Order confirmation/Order review (Order creation with pending status)\n      - Lock inventory with a TTL for user \n\n   \n    Payment Success:\n\n              - Update order confirmation\n\n              - Update inventory (Reduce available quanity), release inventory lock\n\n              - Send Notification\n    \n        \n\nPayment Failure:\n             - Update Order to cancelled, release inventory lock\n             - Send Notification\n\n\nFailure Events: Retries and Compensation mechanisms should be in place\n\n\n              \n\n    ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "yHlBLmqpbJyui_C7J7lQm",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1122.3294648858362,
      "y": 918.9016710908676,
      "width": 1568.8364104350799,
      "height": 1075,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a1",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 36832957,
      "version": 1669,
      "versionNonce": 754091722,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1784520772062,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "APIs:\n\nGET v1/browse/topDeals\n    response:\n            items: {itemId, itemName, itemDescription, unitPrice, currency}\n                    \nGET v1/browse/categories?\"categoryName\"=\"CategoryName\"\n    response:\n        {categoryId, categoryName, items: {itemId, itemName, itemDescription, unitPrice, currency}\n\nGET v1/browse/item/{itemId}\n    items: {itemId, itemName, itemDescription, unitPrice, currency}\n\n\nGET v1/address/{addressId}\n     address: {addressId, addressLine1, addressLine2, pin, city, state, country, phoneNumber, emailId}\n\n\nPOST v1/cart\n      items: {\n                {itemId, itemName, itemDescription, unitPrice, currency, quantity`},\n                {itemId, itemName, itemDescription, unitPrice, currency, quantity`}\n               }\n\n        response {cartId}\n                \n\nPOST v1/orders/placeOrder\n        orderDetails {\n                    cartId,\n                    items: {\n                        {itemId, itemName, itemDescription, unitPrice, currency, quantity`},\n                        {itemId, itemName, itemDescription, unitPrice, currency, quantity`}\n                        }\n                    totalAmount\n                    currency\n                    }\n        response {orderId}\n                    \n                    \n                \n\n    ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "APIs:\n\nGET v1/browse/topDeals\n    response:\n            items: {itemId, itemName, itemDescription, unitPrice, currency}\n                    \nGET v1/browse/categories?\"categoryName\"=\"CategoryName\"\n    response:\n        {categoryId, categoryName, items: {itemId, itemName, itemDescription, unitPrice, currency}\n\nGET v1/browse/item/{itemId}\n    items: {itemId, itemName, itemDescription, unitPrice, currency}\n\n\nGET v1/address/{addressId}\n     address: {addressId, addressLine1, addressLine2, pin, city, state, country, phoneNumber, emailId}\n\n\nPOST v1/cart\n      items: {\n                {itemId, itemName, itemDescription, unitPrice, currency, quantity`},\n                {itemId, itemName, itemDescription, unitPrice, currency, quantity`}\n               }\n\n        response {cartId}\n                \n\nPOST v1/orders/placeOrder\n        orderDetails {\n                    cartId,\n                    items: {\n                        {itemId, itemName, itemDescription, unitPrice, currency, quantity`},\n                        {itemId, itemName, itemDescription, unitPrice, currency, quantity`}\n                        }\n                    totalAmount\n                    currency\n                    }\n        response {orderId}\n                    \n                    \n                \n\n    ",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "IYYCxDxFFVtancUHx1pE6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 337.5,
      "y": 130.5,
      "width": 821.6194458007812,
      "height": 525,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
